OL,6,FAfter the tragedy, the police
OL,7,Finvestigation revealed #1 million was
OL,8,Fbeing sent from the UK to China every
OL,9,Fday, from the exploitation of illegal
OL,10,Fworkers in cockling, sex work and nail
OL,11,Fbars.
OL,13,FFormer DS Gradwell said: "We closed
OL,14,Fdown the gang's banking system but it
OL,15,Fwas quickly up and running again."
OL,17,FWithin days of wages being paid in
OL,18,FMorecambe the money had gone through
OL,19,Fbank accounts in London, before moving
OL,20,Fonto China and to the families.
