OL,6,FBut the largest share went to the
OL,7,Ftraffickers.
OL,9,FIn September 2005, I travelled to
OL,10,FFujian Province in China, where most
OL,11,Fof the victims and their gangmaster
OL,12,Fwere from, to see what drove them to
OL,13,Ftake such risks on the treacherous
OL,14,Fsands at Morecambe Bay.
OL,16,FThe Chinese authorities had denied us
OL,17,Fpermission to film, and the families
OL,18,Fhad been rounded up and warned of
OL,19,Fharsh penalties if they spoke out.
