OL,6,FBut they agreed to meet me, because
OL,7,Fthey were desperate fearing losing
OL,8,Ftheir homes and children.
OL,10,FMost of the workers paid Snakeheads
OL,11,Fbetween #14,000 - #20,000 to smuggle
OL,12,Ftheir loved ones into England through
OL,13,Fcontainers into Liverpool. They were
OL,14,Fthen hired out by agents of Chinese
OL,15,Forganised crime gangs - known as
OL,16,FTriads, with the promise of earning
OL,17,Fhigh wages.
OL,19,FBut the reality was very different.
