OL,4,CMorecambe Bay tragedy 'untouchable'
OL,6,FAfter Guo Bing Long drowned at
OL,7,FMorecambe Bay, his widow told me she
OL,8,Fwas being forced to give up their
OL,9,Fadoptive daughter.
OL,11,FHer husband's family said with the
OL,12,Fmain earner dead, they could not
OL,13,Fafford to look after both her children
OL,14,Fand pay back their debts.
OL,16,FAfter waiting nine months for her
OL,17,Fson's coffin to be sent home to China,
OL,18,FGuo's mother could not cope with their
OL,19,Ffinancial situation and swallowed
OL,20,Fpoison and is now buried alongside her
OL,21,Fson.
