OL,6,FXu Bing was 15 when he was orphaned,
OL,7,Fafter his parents drowned at Morecambe
OL,8,FBay.
OL,10,FHis father had been in Britain for
OL,11,Fseveral years but the family say he
OL,12,Fwas not earning enough to pay their
OL,13,FSnakehead.
OL,15,FHis wife had only been in the country
OL,16,Ffor two weeks when she drowned.
OL,17,FPicking cockles was the only work she
OL,18,Fcould find.
