OL,6,FPolice believe their gangmaster Lin
OL,7,FLiang Ren, a qualified accountant from
OL,8,Fa wealthy family in Fuqing City was
OL,9,Flinked to China's international triad
OL,10,Fsmuggling gangs.
OL,12,FThe traffickers ensured a supply of
OL,13,Findebted workers, and the Gangmaster's
OL,14,Fprovide the employment.
OL,16,FRen was expecting to make #70,000 for
OL,17,Fthe shellfish on the night he forced
OL,18,Fhis workers out on the sands in rising
OL,19,Ftides.
