OL,6,FPaying them as little as #10 for the
OL,7,Fback-breaking work plus charging them
OL,8,Ffor squalid accommodation, with as
OL,9,Fmany as 30 people sharing one bathroom.
OL,11,FIn court, some of the Chinese
OL,12,Fsurvivors who gave evidence against
OL,13,Fthe gangs, said Ren and his cousin Lin
OL,14,FMu Yong would not speak or even look
OL,15,Fat the workers, adding "they were
OL,16,Fbeneath them".
OL,18,FIn March 2006 Lin Liang Ren was
OL,19,Fsentenced for 14 years, serving just
OL,20,Fseven for the manslaughter of 21
OL,21,Fpeople before being deported.
