OL,6,FDuring his trial, his mother Shen Ai
OL,7,FMei agreed to meet me, insisting her
OL,8,Fson was not involved.
OL,10,FShe told me he was working to pay for
OL,11,Fhis studies, and didn't believe he was
OL,12,Fthe gangmaster.
OL,14,FShe said: "I can't believe my son was
OL,15,Fsuch a guy".
OL,17,FHe had spent vast sums gambling in
OL,18,Fcasinos while his countrymen and women
OL,19,Fwere working and paid them a pittance.
