OL,6,FThe court was told if Ren had allowed
OL,7,Fhis workers to come off the beach
OL,8,Fbefore the tide came in, they would
OL,9,Fhave survived.
OL,11,FHis mother insisted: "He was just one
OL,12,Fof the workers there, he shouldn't
OL,13,Ftake responsibility for that."
OL,15,FThe gangmaster's family did not like
OL,16,Fmy questions and reported me to the
OL,17,FChinese authorities, forcing us to
OL,18,Fleave immediately for the airport.
