OL,6,FThey did not want us to share the
OL,7,Fvictims stories, exposing the illegal
OL,8,Ftrade in people.
OL,10,FAt a memorial service to mark the 20th
OL,11,Fanniversary of the tragedy, all 23
OL,12,Fnames of the victims will be read out
OL,13,Fon the beach at Morecambe Bay.
OL,15,FWith a powerful call for action to end
OL,16,Fthe trafficking and exploitation of
OL,17,Fvulnerable people.
